Class ExcelConfig

java.lang.Object
es.urjc.etsii.grafo.io.serializers.AbstractSerializerConfig
es.urjc.etsii.grafo.io.serializers.AbstractResultSerializerConfig
es.urjc.etsii.grafo.io.serializers.excel.ExcelConfig
@SerializerSource @ConfigurationProperties(prefix="serializers.xlsx") public class ExcelConfig extends AbstractResultSerializerConfig
This class is used to configure the Excel serializer by the properties specified in the application.yml Exports the results of each experiment.
